651
00:36:55,700 --> 00:36:56,850
All right. All right.

652
00:36:58,200 --> 00:36:59,350
You know what?

653
00:36:59,350 --> 00:37:00,780
In two more months,

654
00:37:01,040 --> 00:37:02,130
Huolei Plain in Yanbei

655
00:37:02,360 --> 00:37:03,340
