663
00:37:15,530 --> 00:37:16,920
Go back to Yanbei with me.

664
00:37:18,310 --> 00:37:19,750
Could you say something serious?

665
00:37:20,190 --> 00:37:21,670
I am serious.

666
00:37:22,290 --> 00:37:23,700
Since I’m asking,

667
00:37:23,970 --> 00:37:25,180
answer me seriously.

668
00:37:26,250 --> 00:37:26,830
All right?

669
00:37:31,030 --> 00:37:31,920
Here comes my horse.

670
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:34,510
What?

671
00:37:41,690 --> 00:37:42,480
What?

672
00:37:44,020 --> 00:37:44,990
Many people are coming from

673
00:37:44,990 --> 00:37:45,650
your mansion?

674
00:37:47,680 --> 00:37:50,640
And they bring strong weapons.

675
00:37:53,440 --> 00:37:54,900
Little maid.

676
00:37:54,900 --> 00:37:56,000
You’re good.

677
00:38:08,020 --> 00:38:08,940
Let me pull you.

678
00:38:09,100 --> 00:38:09,740
Be careful.

679
00:38:09,900 --> 00:38:10,340
Come.

680
00:38:10,500 --> 00:38:11,180
Watch your step.

681
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:12,140
Mom.

682
00:38:13,660 --> 00:38:14,700
Take my hand.

683
00:38:14,900 --> 00:38:15,660
Be careful.

684
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,450
They ate their words!

685
00:38:17,450 --> 00:38:18,360
Yeah.

686
00:38:18,360 --> 00:38:19,840
They promised to give us
the slave-releasing certificate

687
00:38:19,840 --> 00:38:21,370
after repairing the great wall.

688
00:38:21,370 --> 00:38:22,180
Yeah. Yeah.

689
00:38:22,180 --> 00:38:23,280
Hurry up, guys.

690
00:38:23,280 --> 00:38:24,790
We’re escaping to Yanbei.

691
00:38:24,790 --> 00:38:25,280
Yes.

692
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,300
After we arrive,

693
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,990
we’ll be free.

694
00:38:27,990 --> 00:38:29,340
- Yeah. - Yeah.

695
00:38:29,490 --> 00:38:30,880
Those frauds.

696
00:38:32,900 --> 00:38:35,550
Yeah, they’re frauds.

697
00:38:39,050 --> 00:38:41,190
I can’t walk anymore.

698
00:38:49,670 --> 00:38:51,430
Hurry. Hurry up.

699
00:39:38,440 --> 00:39:39,860
You’re a fraud.

700
00:39:40,110 --> 00:39:41,900
Shameless betrayer.

701
00:39:41,900 --> 00:39:43,960
